page.title: 19A Typical Sunday.
page.content: On Sunday I wake up at 9.00am then I get dressed and eat my breakfast.After that I play games,then at about 11.30 I go in and pack my bag for swimming. It takes me about 15 minutes to get to the pool in which I swim.I spend one and a half hours in my swimming lesson then at 1.45pm I go home then I have a cooked meal.After dinner I go and call for a friend and play with them for 3 hours.Then I come home for tea at 6.00 after that I go out and play until 9.00 then I come in to get ready for bed.
